<div align="center"><h3>Training Services</h3></div>
<div>Engineers Technologies Training Program prepares engineering graduates for the professional world. We provide a solid knowledge and innovation foundation to engineering graduates for Design & Engineering needs of the Automotive, Heavy engineering & other Manufacturing industry.<br/><br/>

We engage industry experts as Associate Mentor and take an active role in Design & Engineering knowledge dissemination & Industry networking for employability of engineering talent.<br/><br/>
Today, India aspires to be a global hub for manufacturing, services, R&D and technology innovations. Global engineering conglomerates are looking towards India for industry aligned talent , which stresses the need for more proactive approach to training as part of a more progressive and comprehensive approach to talent management.<br/><br/>
Aligning with industry essentially means designing & delivering professional training programmes through expert from industry & transferring the knowledge to the aspiring engineering graduates to equip them with industry specific know how, so that companies can employ & deploy them on projects most productively<br/>
